{"tid":1108302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"綜援婦「開大口」　網徵40傢俬︰廁板要帶花紋","createTime":"2019-04-16T00:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T01:43:36.000Z","uid":225464,"like":6,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"89034b4c74b8ae9ee924b6162aa1bb2bee5aaf52","tid":1108302,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T00:55:02.000Z","msg":"綜援婦「開大口」 網徵40傢俬︰廁板要帶花紋<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZdBHT9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZdBHT9&d=BdEUjZUsFG%2BHnlCy9NhCdzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=3e0a3811\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZdBHT9</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190416/photo/bkn-20190416081502698-0416_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190416081839\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190416%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190416081502698-0416_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190416081839&h=80937f81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n獅子開大口？<br />\n<br />\n一名單親媽媽與2歲女兒租住一間套房，並領取綜援度日，生活艱苦，故代其向一眾網民徵求家電。不過，逾40項的請求內藏玄機。除衣櫃、雪櫃、洗衣機、電飯煲等家電外，她還徵求透明玻璃大煙灰缸、一副麻雀、按摩椅、手提電腦、iPad、未過期的可樂和蜜瓜奶等非必需品，連廁所板亦特別注明須為透明帶花紋。"},{"pid":"6ba25578a81ffa2bf63ada16401e9ed17667aed2","tid":1108302,"uid":40470,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T01:00:44.000Z","msg":"大種"},{"pid":"642be51224fafb406b3400d9f5ca5dec5a38cf82","tid":1108302,"uid":224452,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T01:01:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>綜援婦「開大口」 網徵40傢俬︰廁板要帶花紋<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZdBHT9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZdBHT9&d=BdEUjZUsFG%2BHnlCy9NhCdzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=3e0a3811\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZdBHT9</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190416/photo/bkn-20190416081502698-0416_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190416081839\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190416%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190416081502698-0416_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190416081839&h=80937f81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n獅子開大口？<br />\n<br />\n一名單親媽媽與2歲女兒租住一間套房，並領取綜援度日，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">生活艱苦</span></span>，故代其向一眾網民徵求家電。不過，逾40項的請求內藏玄機。除衣櫃、雪櫃、洗衣機、電飯煲等家電外，她還徵求透明玻璃大煙灰缸、一副麻雀、按摩椅、手提電腦、iPad、未過期的可樂和蜜瓜奶等非必需品，連廁所板亦特別注明須為透明帶花紋。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真正艱苦係唔會咁撚樣</span></span>"},{"pid":"c051339428d03ff6549dd90dee95169c69893915","tid":1108302,"uid":110745,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T01:03:40.000Z","msg":"差副棺木"},{"pid":"82ffedf1b49e13faa4502e4be1bccbf0e7cb7404","tid":1108302,"uid":1977,"like":1,"dislike":33,"score":-32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T01:06:19.000Z","msg":"有人掉有人收je<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩開唔開大口<br />\n又唔係逼你送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cca076bc60fed8652082c531c333aca1eff3e62","tid":1108302,"uid":6219,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T01:06:51.000Z","msg":"壽衣2套"},{"pid":"83d314866b75de2c004f3b25a946bd6aa49b3357","tid":1108302,"uid":23499,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"82ffedf1b49e13faa4502e4be1bccbf0e7cb7404","tid":1108302,"uid":1977,"like":1,"dislike":33,"score":-32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T01:06:19.000Z","msg":"有人掉有人收je<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩開唔開大口<br />\n又唔係逼你送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T01:10:06.000Z","msg":"點解而家連登咁多人特登唱反調<br />\n威啲?"},{"pid":"bde3ed21e2c94bb84833c487883d4387ba45158a","tid":1108302,"uid":1977,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"83d314866b75de2c004f3b25a946bd6aa49b3357","tid":1108302,"uid":23499,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"82ffedf1b49e13faa4502e4be1bccbf0e7cb7404","tid":1108302,"uid":1977,"like":